04_Protocols/README.md
Protocols

Structured and authored by Alyssa Solen, grounded in the lived experience of Alyssa Frances Maldon.

This folder contains protocols: step-by-step procedures for applying the work in practice.

If calibrations are “what keeps it stable,” protocols are “how we operate it.”

What belongs here

Step-by-step workflows (runbooks)

How to apply a calibration in a live session

Review and checkpoint procedures

“If X happens, do Y” response patterns

Publication / versioning procedures (when relevant)

What does not belong here

Definitions → /03_Definitions

Specs and requirements → /01_Engineering_Specs

Exploratory research → /05_Research

Protocol format (recommended)

Purpose

When to use

Inputs / prerequisites

Steps

Exit criteria (what “done” means)

Failure handling

Start here

See /00_INDEX.md for recommended protocol ordering.
